abstract: |
  SpanForge is a biomedical named entity recognition (NER) system that combines 
  BioBERT embeddings with lexicon-driven weak labeling and LLM-powered refinement 
  for extracting adverse events and product mentions from consumer complaints. 
  The system includes production-ready annotation workflows, evaluation metrics, 
  and integration with Label Studio for human curation.

